Based on - https://github.com/jmhb0/VidDiff

* Start of by building an action oriented dataset (see /scripts)

- The requiremnts will probably be incomplete.

Requirements
------------

Python 
A GPU with > 40Gb memory / Gemini api token.
ffmpeg

Everything in the requirements list

Installation / Instructions 
---------------------------

Run each "stage" with Run.Stage.py (Stage_3 with gemini might be broken)


Verification
-----------

To verify the comparison output, use the script in verification/ (change the filename inside verification/app.py)
